{"tid":1792920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[手持核彈]星火事件及解放軍不准客機急降","createTime":"2019-12-22T04:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T05:13:16.000Z","uid":3776,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e99f322aae58b5d1b34dfd19db0cc4fc139f67","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"星火擺到明莫須有<br />\n黑警講你洗黑錢就洗黑錢 之後凍結你資產<br />\n今日可以星火 聽日可以係外資<br />\n<br />\n解放軍有咩權可以控制民航局？<br />\n咁樣徹底踐踏左一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n煲大佢啦<br />\n仲係度分化！"},{"pid":"bb0f9c1253df921b29faee894f259fe5b7e2567c","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"咪理啲分化po"},{"pid":"5890f20f34a5590904008b93b23c5996907b8b2a","tid":1792920,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"41099610a1ea8066176fc93d85de0c692631d4c7","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:18:08.000Z","msg":"葉問玩夠啦"},{"pid":"db2e02fcea96efc5a5a6b7cccda3dbbfe8b7b36f","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"煲大佢啦<br />\n上國際新聞"},{"pid":"fd64b86b183b46ac8c392bd4f65f077e64aadd69","tid":1792920,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zjT1qE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zjT1qE.jpg&h=f1f65c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日三點半，麻煩大家準時！<br />\n現場唔好有連豬，連狗<br />\n尊重返人哋啲宗教<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAHBZcu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAHBZcu.gif&h=f5f36c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpRGqSx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpRGqSx.gif&h=bc12f105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，&Ouml;zil畀人屌到屎眼爛都冇跪<br />\n我哋聽日都要支持佢<br />\n<br />\nStand with Uyghur(We ga）, Stand with &Ouml;zil（奧燒）"},{"pid":"a3288f7ab60d2a92cc97d2e2de876c433d98f1e5","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"外資快撤<br />\n唔係就凍結你資產<br />\n再送你中"},{"pid":"a4053aabba52491ec9436d25b145feec3387f1e4","tid":1792920,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:19:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3a65373e2b86abfa71543da599712bcefbd0d2d9","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"有無巴打整文宣！<br />\n我英文唔夠好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有巴打出手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47659e13b871da5608070aad88ef977e5cb14181","tid":1792920,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b2e92ef316bdbd6224a843ff9d2f1444904300c4","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"推啦 正係一味識分化"},{"pid":"1e9494874a016bbb43ed14e15a4c8e92944ccb67","tid":1792920,"uid":179380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"#不是劇透 #必須看到尾<br />\n#入戲院前你要知的小背景<br />\n<br />\n【無雷】你不能不知道的＜葉問4＞基礎認識<br />\n<br />\n葉問得了癌症，偏偏兒子不學好，在學校打架鬧事，慘遭學校退學。葉問只好接受弟子李小龍的邀請，去美國為兒子申請學校，豈知華人到了美國受盡歧視，處處碰壁。<br />\n<br />\n李小龍於美國出書，收鬼佬徒弟教功夫，引起唐人街華人武術界不滿。李小龍因此得罪了中華總會會長萬宗華。葉問與萬會長相識之初，因為對於中華傳統武術意見不合，隨即展開了一場詠春對戰太極的戲碼，萬會長發現葉問受傷了，直接收起一隻手跟對方打。<br />\n<br />\n葉問拿不到萬會長的推薦信，無法讓兒子葉正入學。人在異鄉的葉問很想聽到兒子的聲音，可是每次的長途電話都被兒子拒絕接聽，父子關係惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n這時，李小龍的美軍徒弟吳建豪，想將詠春引入美國部隊，受空手道教官打壓，派人去唐人街踢館，被葉問狠狠教訓，挑起了美國海軍陸戰隊跟唐人街的仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n美國軍官趁著中秋晚會把會長綁走，並且打趴了所有會中的武師，找移民局拉人。這時葉問出馬，打趴了挑釁的美國人，美國人又把會長綁入海軍陸戰隊，並且打到重傷。葉問看不下去，認為中國人不能再被欺侮，於是叫吳建豪把他帶入海軍陸戰隊，美國人跟葉問一番激戰之後，再度打趴美國人。<br />\n<br />\n葉問解救了中華總會的貌美女兒若男，但還是無法讓萬宗華會長點頭寫推薦信。<br />\n<br />\n於是，葉問放棄了兒子的留學計劃，決定回香港並與兒子和好，教授兒子葉正畢生絕學，還叫他兒子用機器拍攝。最後，葉問在79歲因癌症去世，畫面切換至徒弟李小龍祭拜，然後開始播放前幾集畫面，包括洪金寶、黃曉明、熊黛林等場景。全劇完。<br />\n<br />\n#不是劇透<br />\n#不要share<br />\n#share了觀眾便不會購票"},{"pid":"f345b14663d457a484d82d5dea54943ba7a42f04","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd64b86b183b46ac8c392bd4f65f077e64aadd69","tid":1792920,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zjT1qE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zjT1qE.jpg&h=f1f65c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日三點半，麻煩大家準時！<br />\n現場唔好有連豬，連狗<br />\n尊重返人哋啲宗教<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAHBZcu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAHBZcu.gif&h=f5f36c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpRGqSx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpRGqSx.gif&h=bc12f105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，&Ouml;zil畀人屌到屎眼爛都冇跪<br />\n我哋聽日都要支持佢<br />\n<br />\nStand with Uyghur(We ga）, Stand with &Ouml;zil（奧燒）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"stand with uyghur!"},{"pid":"0a1b6cae3439bc530e11c1f541f0d14826fabbf1","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 各自努力"},{"pid":"7c525aff697b389297b2fc34ec123c3c23be7d46","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"其實有無得去信各大外資公司<br />\n闡述禍害 叫佢撤資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21eeea6e7aca3fe07e77929daa3e01fe3b60a626","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"推上去推上熱門"},{"pid":"26a5e7cc651feadae77bf53d89616fd9d140acfc","tid":1792920,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa